<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>ر ش ش<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[٢١٠٩ - ر ش ش]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>رشَّ رشَشْتُ، يَرُشّ، ارْشُشْ/ رُشَّ، رَشًّا، فهو راشّ،<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>⦗٨٩٦⦘ والمفعول مرشوش <span class="c2">(للمتعدِّي)</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">• رشَّت السَّماءُ:</span> أمطرت ° رشَّت العين: دَمَعَت.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5">• رشَّ الشَّيءَ:</span> نثَره وذرَّه <span class="c1">"رشّ مِلحًا/ كيماويّات"</span>.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c5">• رشَّ الماءَ:</span> نفَضه وفرَّقه.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c5">• رشَّه بالماء:</span> نضَحه وبلَّه <span class="c1">"رشَّ الأرض والزرع بالماء- رشَّ الطريقَ بالماء"</span>.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>